{"tid":1124370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：公民抗命非「大富翁出獄證」","createTime":"2019-04-25T04:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T04:57:51.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4b68e952c47bd4bdd109a41915ea2657c037dda8","tid":1124370,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:03:10.000Z","msg":"資深大律師的行會成員湯家驊其後接受節目訪問時稱，判刑是預料之內，但對仍有人認為可用「公民抗命」為答辯理由感些許詫異。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊解釋，根據黃之鋒案的終審庭判辭，當時終審庭法官已闡明「公民抗命」並非答辯理由，因行駛自由與違法不可並立，「即使你的理念多麽崇高，你都是犯法」，故強調「公民抗命」並非等同「免死金牌」或「大富翁出獄證」，認為有關人等可能沒看清楚黃之鋒案的判辭。"},{"pid":"5585f4f417690a8ba8022a85e79170f446ac7a14","tid":1124370,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:04:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190425/s00001/1556159155629/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190425%2Fs00001%2F1556159155629%2F&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=7a5f8955\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190425%2Fs00001%2F1556159155629%2F&h=3e873a3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190425/s00001/1556159155629/</a>"},{"pid":"8bc9e46e99f12bc164b92c5e736f74e8a245f244","tid":1124370,"uid":61882,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">淚</span></span>"},{"pid":"432bc4bea7ff91e2b8f6d0ce77a9ae90478a8c9b","tid":1124370,"uid":85629,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:05:36.000Z","msg":"投共是否就某些嚴重性罪行之免死金牌"},{"pid":"5101572ee1550ed2f83e941dc4c71b020ab0ed5b","tid":1124370,"uid":137217,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:06:55.000Z","msg":"含撚啦湯家驊"},{"pid":"b494496b7e5386d13c9e4738ffa48a2f48fbdad8","tid":1124370,"uid":31237,"like":1,"dislike":0,